# Exclude Python backend — not deployed on Vercel (runs on HuggingFace Spaces)
# Without this, Vercel tries to build api/*.py as serverless functions,
# fails (no requirements.txt for torch/FastAPI), and silently stops auto-deploys.
#
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT exclude the api/ directory as a whole — api/*.js are
# Edge Functions (waitlist, health). Exclude only Python files inside api/.
api/*.py
mcp/
glassbox/
dashboard/
tests/
scripts/
requirements/
*.py
*.toml
*.cfg
*.ini
